Description:

libcap is now used by default if it's available


Documentation:

There isn't any, except perhaps the libcap documentation


Config changes:

None


Upgrade instructions:

If you want libcap support, make sure you have libcap and the corresponding
-dev package installed.  On Debian Bookworm, these are `libcap2` and
`libcap-dev`.

If you do not want libcap support, pass `--without-libcap` to configure.


GitHub issue:

None
